{"type": "article", "id": 10109, "title": "Adidas Mid Summer Weave 系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-28T07:24:38Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 42, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135133F24YtQ7Iuqj9SEmO.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t随着 Stan Smith 广受大家的喜爱，Adidas Originals 也在不遗余力地为 Stan Smith 家族添砖加瓦，最近，他们推出了一个新的 Mid Summer Weave 系列，采用清凉的编织材料，专门为适合炎热的夏季。保留 Stan Smith 精髓，目前有红色，蓝色和银色三款颜色，造型简单时尚。这款鞋子将于今年 6 月 1 日开始 Adidas Originals 全球门店开始发售。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135131RCdUlZuAyE4hD15B.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061351316vVg02xpKnMG4ryA.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135132HobYwEFZzgxeQpBd.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}